{"tid":555011,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣婉拒中國大陸協助地震救災　中國大陸網友：不知好歹","createTime":"2018-02-09T04:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T04:59:15.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f921c3a135614162b9c9c8789b901250b45e1036","tid":555011,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:53:52.000Z","msg":"台婉拒陸方協助地震救災　陸網友：不知好歹<br />\n<br />\n2018/02/09 08:19<br />\n<br />\n花蓮發生強震災情後，中國大陸政府表示願意提供援助，但遭我政府婉拒。中國大陸網友發現我國僅接受來自日方協助後，紛紛留言批評台灣政府。<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸新浪網今早出現一則花蓮震災新聞，標題為「台當局拒絕大陸援助花蓮震災 卻唯獨向日本求助」。該新聞內容報導台灣政府婉拒大陸派出救援隊的提議，僅接受日本救難協助，因其擁有「高階探測儀」。<br />\n<br />\n新聞下方出現許多大陸網友留言，有人寫著：「熱臉又貼上冷屁股！」、「別理他不知好歹」、「蔡果然是小日本親生的」、「到台灣找死？」、「好，免得又要搞賑災捐款」。<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180209/1295268/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180209%2F1295268%2F&d=g2lStspYMc9BVbsoXhqxw8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4ccc522f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180209%2F1295268%2F&h=f0477b6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180209/1295268/</a>"},{"pid":"2da475dcf2c8d2699fd6142e2f9b4a68a13a2d7b","tid":555011,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82740f7c3849c5008884a02df8fb8119f62c1a7d","tid":555011,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"Fuckin snowflake"}]}